body_html: @zgsxwsdxg which platform, which OpenCV version, which TF commit hash, and are you linking to anything besides libtensorflow_cc.so? Those symbols should be locked down pretty well (https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/tf_exported_symbols.lds or https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/tf_version_script.lds depending on the platform).
